r />\n利申全程冇爆粗，聲浪適中</blockquote><br />\n閃閃下好似係唔過得。同場仲要有差佬....<br />\nPass比差佬你點嘈都入硬你<br />\n<br />\n利申，老豆中左伏，不過係差佬捉。同場有幾個學生哥都照罰錢。"},{"pid":"a01b7c3aa5ed8286dd3cd2e57866df31c6ded2f8","tid":345542,"uid":35285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10ff3170fa7d1ded065f6839028d438896270e3d","tid":345542,"uid":93217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然係咁 如果黑警在場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食硬</blockquote><br />\n當時有幾多黑警係附近<br />\n其實都淆，如果佢真係pass比黑警會點？未遇過</blockquote><br />\n黑警唔會理係未佢屈你，佢地一定會幫佢，要你出示身分證，你唔肯就拉你阻差辦工"},{"pid":"d0ab93b10d05492ca013ec16d5f4a8ffd180af74","tid":345542,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>竟然係咁 如果黑警在場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食硬</blockquote><br />\n當時有幾多黑警係附近<br />\n其實都淆，如果佢真係pass比黑警會點？未遇過</blockquote><br />\n黑警唔會理係未佢屈你，佢地一定會幫佢，要你出示身分證，你唔肯就拉你阻差辦工</blockquote><br />\n你係佢都唔理啦係嘛<br />\n<br />\n人地department捉人關我鬼事？"},{"pid":"fe994f4388027628051795a33d87e3c2f8d0d9b1","tid":345542,"uid":39245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪撚quote條死on9得唔撚得阿？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實條友都幾撚煩<br />\n點解可以keep住咁多負皮都繼續可以次次頭幾個就回到<br />\n<br />\n面皮厚到可以同袁生做fd"},{"pid":"f84ac3cb429316f450394245a590962293e2d67a","tid":345542,"uid":70901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"冇奶油咁都唔拍片"},{"pid":"dc8e34e82cf13bce66ab217bc7c98e298e41e18f","tid":345542,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebda2ba66deb87b8bfc028